{"article_id":"IIYkIW9TLwVWtoQG","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"FILE -","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"In this Dec. 2 , 2019 , file photo , Lev Parnas arrives at court in New York .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"Parnas , a close associate of President Donald Trump 's personal lawyer , Rudy Giuliani , has provided a trove of text messages and photos to the House committee","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"leading the impeachment inquiry .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"( AP Photo/Seth Wenig , File )","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"FILE -","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"In this Dec. 2 , 2019 , file photo , Lev Parnas arrives at court in New York .","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"Parnas , a close associate of President Donald Trump 's personal lawyer , Rudy Giuliani , has provided a trove of text messages and photos to the House committee","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"leading the impeachment inquiry .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"( AP Photo/Seth Wenig , File )","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"WASHINGTON","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"( AP ) -","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"A close associate of President Donald Trump ' s personal lawyer Rudy Giuliani is claiming","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"Trump was directly involved in the effort","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"to pressure Ukraine to investigate Democratic rival Joe Biden .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Lev Parnas says","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"he delivered an ultimatum in May , at Giuliani ' s behest , to the incoming president of Ukraine","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"that no senior U.S. officials would attend his inauguration","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"and vital American security aid would be withheld","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"if an investigation into Biden wasn ' t announced .","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"Trump was aware of Giuliani ' s efforts","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"to secure an investigation","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"and the president was briefed regularly .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"If true ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Parnas ' account undercuts a key Republican defense of Trump during the impeachment investigation","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"- that Trump ' s withholding of vital military aid to Ukraine last summer wasn ' t a quid pro quo for Biden investigations .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"\" President Trump knew exactly what was going on , \"","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"said Parnas , a Soviet-born Florida businessman","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"facing a raft of criminal charges","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"related to campaign finance violations .","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"\" He was aware of all my movements .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"I wouldn ' t do anything","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"without the consent of Rudy Giuliani , or the president . \"","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"Parnas made several potentially explosive claims in a televised interview Wednesday night with MSNBC ' s Rachel Maddow .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"The day after","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"Parnas said","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"he delivered the message ,","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"the State Department announced","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"that Vice President Mike Pence would no longer be attending the inauguration of Ukrainian President Volodymir Zelenskiy .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"Parnas alleged","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"that Trump ordered Pence to stay away at the behest of Giuliani","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"to send a clear message to the incoming Ukrainian administration","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"that they needed to take seriously the demand for an investigation into Biden , a Democratic presidential candidate","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"seen as a potential threat to Trump ' s 2020 reelection .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Parnas said","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"every communication","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"he had with Zelenskiy ' s team","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"was at the direction of Giuliani ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"whom he regularly overheard briefing Trump about their progress by phone .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"\" I feel sorry for him , \"","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"Giuliani said Wednesday in a text message to an AP reporter .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"\" I thought","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"he was an honorable man .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"I was wrong . \"","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Asked directly","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"if Parnas was lying ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"Trump ' s lawyer replied ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"\" I ' m not responding yet . \"","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"Parnas said","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"he also heard Giuliani and another Trump-aligned defense lawyer , Victoria Toensing , briefing Attorney General William Barr by phone about their efforts","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"to pressure the Ukrainian government to announce the investigation into Biden and his son Hunter ' s business dealings .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"The Justice Department said in September","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"that Trump had not spoken to Barr","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"about having Ukraine investigate the Bidens","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"and that the attorney general had not discussed Ukraine with Giuliani .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"Justice Department spokeswoman Kerri Kupec said Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"that Parnas ' claims were \" 100 % false . \"","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"The new accusations came","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"as House Democrats made public a trove of documents , text messages and photos from Parnas ' smartphones","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"that appear to verify parts of his account .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"The documents ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"released just ahead of the start of the impeachment trial ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"could raise pressure on the Senate","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"as it debates whether to hear witnesses .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"A federal judge earlier this month ruled","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"that Parnas could provide the materials to Congress as part of the impeachment proceedings .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"Democrats voted in December to impeach Trump for abuse of power and for obstruction of Congress .","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"A House committee chairman said","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"his panel will investigate what he says","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"are \" profoundly alarming \" text messages among the newly disclosed materials","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"that have raised questions about the possible surveillance of former Ambassador to Ukraine Marie Yovanovitch","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"before she was ousted by the Trump administration last spring .","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"The messages show","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"that Robert F. Hyde , a Republican candidate for Congress from Connecticut , disparaged Yovanovitch in messages to Parnas","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"and gave him updates on her location and cellphone use .","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"Rep. Eliot Engel , D_N.Y. ,","depth":16},{"id":87,"text":"who chairs the House Foreign Affairs Committee ,","depth":16},{"id":88,"text":"said","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"the messages are \" profoundly alarming \"","depth":15},{"id":90,"text":"and \" suggest a possible risk \" to Yovanovitch ' s security in Kyiv","depth":16},{"id":91,"text":"before she was recalled from her post .","depth":16},{"id":92,"text":"\" These threats occurred at the same time","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"that the two men were also discussing President Trump ' s efforts ,","depth":17},{"id":94,"text":"through Rudy Giuliani ,","depth":17},{"id":95,"text":"to smear the ambassador ' s reputation , \"","depth":16},{"id":96,"text":"Engel said .","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"He said","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"the committee is seeking assurances","depth":14},{"id":99,"text":"that proper steps have been taken","depth":15},{"id":100,"text":"to ensure the security of Yovanovitch and committee staff .","depth":15},{"id":101,"text":"The text and phone records show","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"Parnas communicating with Giuliani multiple times a day before Yovanovitch ' s removal , as well as a handwritten note","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"that mentions","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"asking Ukraine ' s president to investigate \" the Biden case . \"","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"Among the documents is a screenshot of a previously undisclosed letter from Giuliani to Zelenskiy","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"dated May 10 , 2019 ,","depth":15},{"id":107,"text":"which was shortly after Zelenskiy was elected","depth":16},{"id":108,"text":"but before he took office .","depth":16},{"id":109,"text":"In the letter , Giuliani requests a meeting with Zelenskiy \" as personal counsel to President Trump and with his knowledge and consent . \"","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"The reported in October","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"that Zelenskiy had huddled three days earlier , on May 7 , with a small group of key advisers in Kyiv","depth":15},{"id":112,"text":"to seek advice","depth":16},{"id":113,"text":"about how to navigate the insistence from Trump and Giuliani for a probe into the Bidens .","depth":16},{"id":114,"text":"He expressed his unease","depth":16},{"id":115,"text":"about becoming entangled in the American elections ,","depth":16},{"id":116,"text":"according to three people familiar with the details of the three-hour meeting .","depth":15},{"id":117,"text":"They spoke on the condition of anonymity","depth":15},{"id":118,"text":"because of the diplomatic sensitivity of the issue ,","depth":16},{"id":119,"text":"which has roiled U.S.-Ukrainian relations .","depth":16},{"id":120,"text":"One of the documents","depth":15},{"id":121,"text":"released by Democrats","depth":15},{"id":122,"text":"is a note from Parnas","depth":16},{"id":123,"text":"handwritten on stationery from the Ritz-Carlton Hotel in Vienna","depth":16},{"id":124,"text":"that says","depth":16},{"id":125,"text":"\" get Zalensky to Annonce","depth":17},{"id":126,"text":"that the Biden case will be Investigated . \"","depth":17},{"id":127,"text":"Parnas told Maddow","depth":15},{"id":128,"text":"he took the notes","depth":15},{"id":129,"text":"as he was speaking by phone to Giuliani ,","depth":15},{"id":130,"text":"receiving precise instructions about the demands","depth":16},{"id":131,"text":"Trump wanted to convey to Zelenskiy ' s team .","depth":16},{"id":132,"text":"Trump asked Zelenskiy in a July 25 call to investigate the Bidens .","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"Hunter Biden served on the board of a gas company","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"based in Ukraine .","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"Parnas and his business partner , Igor Fruman , both U.S. citizens","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"who emigrated from the former Soviet Union ,","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"were indicted last year on charges of conspiracy , making false statements and falsification of records .","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"Prosecutors allege","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"they made outsize campaign donations to Republican causes","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"after receiving millions of dollars","depth":14},{"id":141,"text":"originating from Russia .","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"The men have pleaded not guilty .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"Parnas ' lawyer , Joseph Bondy , told The New York Times","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"that his client is looking to cooperate with prosecutors in his case ,","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"who are investigating Giuliani and his dealings in Ukraine .","depth":14},{"id":146,"text":"\" We very much want to provide substantial assistance to the government , \"","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"Bondy told the Times .","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"Parnas told the newspaper","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"that","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"although he didn ' t speak with Trump directly about the efforts ,","depth":15},{"id":151,"text":"he met with the president on several occasions","depth":16},{"id":152,"text":"and was told by Giuliani","depth":17},{"id":153,"text":"that Trump was kept in the loop .","depth":17},{"id":154,"text":"In several of the documents , Parnas communicated with Giuliani about the removal of Yovanovitch .","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"The ambassador ' s ouster ,","depth":16},{"id":156,"text":"ordered by Trump ,","depth":16},{"id":157,"text":"was at the center of the Democrats ' impeachment inquiry .","depth":15},{"id":158,"text":"Yovanovitch testified in the House impeachment hearings","depth":17},{"id":159,"text":"that she was the victim of a \" smear campaign . \"","depth":17},{"id":160,"text":"Trump on the July call told Zelenskiy","depth":17},{"id":161,"text":"that Yovanovitch was \" going to go through some things. \"","depth":17},{"id":162,"text":"She had been recalled from her diplomatic post roughly three months earlier .","depth":15},{"id":163,"text":"On April 23 ,","depth":15},{"id":164,"text":"just before Yovanovitch was directed to return to the United States ,","depth":16},{"id":165,"text":"Giuliani texted Parnas ,","depth":16},{"id":166,"text":"\" He fired her again. \"","depth":14},{"id":167,"text":"Parnas texted back ,","depth":15},{"id":168,"text":"\" I pray","depth":16},{"id":169,"text":"it happens this time","depth":16},{"id":170,"text":"I ' ll call you tomorrow my brother . \"","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"After texting about the ambassador ,","depth":14},{"id":172,"text":"Hyde gave Parnas detailed updates","depth":15},{"id":173,"text":"that suggested","depth":16},{"id":174,"text":"he was watching her .","depth":16},{"id":175,"text":"In one text , Hyde wrote :","depth":15},{"id":176,"text":"\" She ' s talked to three people .","depth":17},{"id":177,"text":"Her phone is off .","depth":18},{"id":178,"text":"Her computer is off. \"","depth":18},{"id":179,"text":"He said","depth":17},{"id":180,"text":"she was under heavy security","depth":18},{"id":181,"text":"and \" we have a person inside . \"","depth":18},{"id":182,"text":"Hyde texted Parnas","depth":15},{"id":183,"text":"that ''they are willing to help","depth":17},{"id":184,"text":"if we/you would like a price , \"","depth":17},{"id":185,"text":"and \" guess","depth":18},{"id":186,"text":"you can do anything in Ukraine with money ...","depth":18},{"id":187,"text":"is what I was told . \"","depth":17},{"id":188,"text":"Lawrence Robbins , an attorney for Yovanovitch , called for an investigation into the messages .","depth":11},{"id":189,"text":"In a Twitter post Tuesday , Hyde called Parnas a \" dweeb \"","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"and suggested","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"the messages","depth":14},{"id":192,"text":"about surveilling the ambassador","depth":14},{"id":193,"text":"were a joke .","depth":13},{"id":194,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":195,"text":"he welcomed an investigation .","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"Parnas , in turn , also said Wednesday","depth":10},{"id":197,"text":"that Hyde ' s texts shouldn ' t be taken seriously .","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"The text messages show","depth":6},{"id":199,"text":"that Parnas consulted Giuliani in January 2019","depth":7},{"id":200,"text":"after the U.S. denied a visa to former Ukrainian Prosecutor General Viktor Shokin .","depth":7},{"id":201,"text":"Giuliani replied :","depth":7},{"id":202,"text":"\" I can revive it . \"","depth":7},{"id":203,"text":"The following day , Giuliani told Parnas ,","depth":8},{"id":204,"text":"\" It ' s going to work","depth":9},{"id":205,"text":"I have no 1 in it. \"","depth":9},{"id":206,"text":"Giuliani then predicted","depth":9},{"id":207,"text":"\" he will get one , \"","depth":9},{"id":208,"text":"before giving Parnas the phone number for Jay Sekulow , the leader of the president ' s personal legal team .","depth":9},{"id":209,"text":"Sekulow is expected to be part of Trump ' s legal team during the impeachment trial .","depth":9},{"id":210,"text":"Trump has repeatedly denied","depth":7},{"id":211,"text":"knowing Parnas and Fruman ,","depth":7},{"id":212,"text":"despite numerous photos","depth":7},{"id":213,"text":"that have emerged of the men together .","depth":7},{"id":214,"text":"Among the materials","depth":7},{"id":215,"text":"released from Parnas ' phone this week","depth":7},{"id":216,"text":"were more photos of him with Trump , as well as the president ' s son Donald Trump Jr. , first daughter Ivanka Trump , and her husband , Jared Kushner .","depth":6},{"id":217,"text":"Asked by Maddow about Trump ' s denials","depth":7},{"id":218,"text":"of knowing him ,","depth":7},{"id":219,"text":"Parnas said","depth":7},{"id":220,"text":"he had spoken one-on-one with the president numerous times .","depth":7},{"id":221,"text":"\" He lied , \"","depth":7},{"id":222,"text":"Parnas said of the president .","depth":7},{"id":223,"text":"\" I mean ,","depth":8},{"id":224,"text":"we ' re not friends .","depth":8},{"id":225,"text":"Me and him didn ' t watch football games together ,","depth":9},{"id":226,"text":"we didn ' t eat hot dogs .","depth":9},{"id":227,"text":"But he knew exactly who we were ,","depth":9},{"id":228,"text":"who I was especially . \"","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":457,"left":238,"right":456,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":238,"left":233,"right":237,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":233,"left":0,"right":232,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":232,"left":1,"right":231,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":231,"left":230,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":230,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":237,"left":234,"right":236,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":234,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":236,"left":235,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":235,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":456,"left":295,"right":455,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":295,"left":262,"right":294,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":262,"left":239,"right":261,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":239,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":261,"left":260,"right":34,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":260,"left":250,"right":259,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250,"left":241,"right":249,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":12,"right":240,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":240,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":249,"left":245,"right":248,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":245,"left":15,"right":244,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":244,"left":16,"right":243,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":243,"left":242,"right":19,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":248,"left":20,"right":247,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":247,"left":246,"right":23,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":246,"left":21,"right":22,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":252,"right":258,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":24,"right":251,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":251,"left":25,"right":26,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":258,"left":255,"right":257,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":255,"left":27,"right":254,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":254,"left":28,"right":253,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":29,"right":30,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":257,"left":31,"right":256,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":256,"left":32,"right":33,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":294,"left":266,"right":293,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":266,"left":264,"right":265,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":264,"left":35,"right":263,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":263,"left":36,"right":37,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":265,"left":38,"right":39,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":293,"left":270,"right":292,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":270,"left":40,"right":269,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":269,"left":41,"right":268,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":42,"right":267,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":43,"right":44,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":286,"right":291,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":286,"left":279,"right":285,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":274,"right":278,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":45,"right":273,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":273,"left":271,"right":272,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":271,"left":46,"right":47,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":48,"right":49,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":275,"right":277,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":275,"left":50,"right":51,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":276,"right":54,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":276,"left":52,"right":53,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":285,"left":282,"right":284,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":282,"left":280,"right":281,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":280,"left":55,"right":56,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":281,"left":57,"right":58,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":284,"left":59,"right":283,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":283,"left":60,"right":61,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":291,"left":289,"right":290,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":62,"right":288,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":288,"left":287,"right":65,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":287,"left":63,"right":64,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":66,"right":67,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":455,"left":436,"right":454,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":436,"left":424,"right":435,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":424,"left":303,"right":423,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":303,"left":301,"right":302,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":301,"left":297,"right":300,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":297,"left":68,"right":296,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":296,"left":69,"right":70,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":298,"right":299,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":298,"left":71,"right":72,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":299,"left":73,"right":74,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":302,"left":75,"right":76,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":423,"left":77,"right":422,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":422,"left":359,"right":421,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":359,"left":357,"right":358,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":357,"left":325,"right":356,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":325,"left":307,"right":324,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":307,"left":78,"right":306,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":306,"left":79,"r